Popcorn.gif
[[Image:Popcorn.gif|frame|right|The original.]]
[[Image:Popcorn.jpg|frame|200px|right|Jpg form]]
'''Popcorn.gif''' is a mild trolling technique used to highlight drama and a faggotry in a forum or journal comment thread. The would-be troll posts an animated gif from a TV show, movie etc of someone eating popcorn.

==Origins==

As with all [[retard|retarded]] [[meme|memes]], this one appears to be another gem from [[Jameth|Jameth's]] [[LiveJournal]], in which someone responded to a suspenseful post with an animated gif of [[Pedophile|Michael Jackson]] eating popcorn and smiling [[Insane Clown Posse|creepily]].

